{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18d3", "eventName": "覆潮之下", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SV-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "守護者", "storyInfo": "斯卡蒂下定決心，應主教邀請，前去教堂。與此同時，審判官決定炸毀教堂。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibtownn"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_180#3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天拿的夠多了吧？除了我、佩特拉奶奶、長凳的份......", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，還有歌手，歌手還會回來的吧？也不能讓她餓肚子。", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剩下的......還有多。可以存盒子裡。", "name": "安妮塔"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，壁爐叔，你想要嗎？那、那我還是先給你。", "name": "安妮塔"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇哇，你胳膊上纏著的這些好像是海藻欸！給我吧，我要試試做歌手教我的......呃，海藻酒！", "name": "安妮塔"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_180#2"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，長凳呢？一晃眼又跑哪裡去了？", "name": "安妮塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_180#2"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咿呀......啊......", "name": "幼年居民"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4", "fadetime": 0.6}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "一道紅色的身影出現在他跟前。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......歌......啊啊......", "name": "幼年居民"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別抓。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個給你。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚哇......", "name": "幼年居民"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別啃。不能吃。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "木框，木框......", "name": "幼年居民"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別叫她。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，你幫我把琴帶給她。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴她......不，你沒法告訴她。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這還不是再見。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去問問題。然後，我會自己說。", "name": "斯卡蒂"}, "figure_art": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#4"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "斯卡蒂的目光投向高處的教堂。她清楚剩下的路該怎麼走。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibcoastn"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，我們現在就要在山體上安置爆破物嗎？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一方面，我看見一個人進了教堂。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看起來和我們之前遇見過的那個外來人......很像。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#2"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，長官，她到底是什麼人？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿戈爾人。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#2"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說了，她和恐魚戰鬥了。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......除了我們之外，竟然還有人知道這些怪物，專門和這些怪物戰鬥......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我們炸毀教堂......她會受到波及嗎？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不解決首惡，將這裡毀滅也無用。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#2"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣嗎？所以還是得知道，是誰在這裡引起了異象......長官也不能確定嗎？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不可問你任務之外的事。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......明白了。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，雖然我知道長官你不在意，但我還是想說說......這個區塊的承重結構，承受不住我們設計的爆炸的威力。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "南半側的城市隨時都可能塌陷，這裡的居民卻還不知道這個消息。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續說。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#3"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想去疏散他們。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕他們在長官你看來是古怪的，有問題的......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......應該被淨化的。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "判官！", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#5"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#5"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說出你的職責！", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#4"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#4"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我是為了伊比利亞的存續，為了同伊比利亞的敵人而戰，為了守衛伊比利亞的潔淨與德行，提起了劍與燈！”", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#4"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼你必須對他們做出判決！", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#5"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "判決？判處他們......死刑嗎？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#5"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#2"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，你上一次聽到過去的歌聲，是什麼時候？那些唱片，都已經壞了吧？你的機器也落灰很久了吧？", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽見那首歌。我聽見了這個阿戈爾人給他們唱的歌。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的歌，是伊比利亞原本該有的歌。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#3"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在殺死他們以前，我想知道真相。就像長官你想揪出幕後主使者。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許他們還是會變異，到那時候，我一定會親手淨化他們，但現在我想讓他們先去避難。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，如果你同意，我立刻就會去進行疏散！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你的判決？", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#3"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，我不知道！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾麗妮，你不止在對面前的人下判決。你也在對其他人下判決！", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你判決怪物生，就是判決人民死！", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#3"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白！這樣的判決，我已經下過許多次！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的判決，既可能阻絕災難，也可能帶來噩兆！你可能救一人而殺百人，也可能殺百人而救一人！", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#3"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我明白，長官！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡面的利害關係，道德和經文的衝突......我都明白！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問你這個了嗎？", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#2"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問你的是，艾麗妮，這種責任是你能承擔得了的嗎？", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你會帶來痛苦，你就必須也遭受痛苦，而且要比你施加給別人的那些罪惡加起來還要多。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你有這種膽識嗎？你的信仰會在你遭受內心折磨時動搖嗎？如果你失敗了，你造成了惡果，你會因此一蹶不振嗎？", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#3"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我能承擔。我不會動搖。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我加入審判庭的時候，我就已經這麼做了。我能。如果我做錯了，那麼就讓我遭受責罰。我必須做。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官！我——", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#3"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以了。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#5"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#5"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以了。現在去履行你的職責，判官。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#4"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——是，長官！我立刻就去疏散當地居民！", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#4"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，長官......經匣裡剩下的爆破物應該夠炸毀整座鹽風城。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#4"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#2"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以......", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#2"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如有必要，你的判決將被我廢除。", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#6"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#6"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_182#4"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我去了，老師。", "name": "審判官艾麗妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_182#4"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_183#3"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "艾麗妮風一般地跑開了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "大審判官矗立原地，如同海邊的礁石。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "當判官心有疑問，他們才有機會追索答案。只是對於面前這個還沒經歷過多少醜惡與幻覺的年輕女孩來說，這一切都太早了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她還要受錘打，還要淬煉。她得失敗過，崩潰過。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她要受苦，她要放棄她不切實際的願景，才會堅韌不拔。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "......", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "等等。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰？", "name": "大審判官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_183#3"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_003_kalts_1", "blackstart": 0.2, "blackend": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，大審判官閣下。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ibchurch"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$jealous_intro", "key": "$jealous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1012_skadiSP_1#1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_184"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，看看是誰來了。", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歡迎你，吟遊歌手。", "name": "主教"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_184"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}